||=====================
|| Wallbox Mobile Flow
||=====================

	** Wallbox User :
		- user will register and login.
		- can see the wallbox order which he buy from the website.
		- can see the subscription which he buy from the website.
		- can see the installation records.

		- can see the charging station (means charger).
		- can see the session records.
		- can see the logs records.

		- can see the own 'request charging' records and 'request charging' in which he is set as a 
		  wallbox owner.

		- can see own 'sale order' records and 'sale orders' in which he is set as salesperson.

		- can see own invoices and invoices which is created by the user.

		** For Charging request
			- select a serial number or scan a serial number or manually enter a serial number.
			- select a vehicle. 
			- and click on confirm, it will create a charging request in odoo.

			if in the charging request, user select it's own wallbox serial
				- user need to add the schedule datetime for start the charging.

			- user will click on start charging.

			- if 'start charging' then request status = 'in_progress'
				if in_progress - visible 'Complete charging' btn for stop charging.

			- when the charging stop request status = 'completed'

	** Guest User :
		** For Charging request
			- select a serial number or scan a serial number or manually enter a serial number.
			- select a vehicle. 
			- and click on confirm, it will create a charging request in odoo.


			if in the charging request, user select wallbox serial and wallbox is not it's own and user is not in allowed_partner_ids.
				- user need to request approval from wallbox owner

			- user will click on 'request charging'.
				- request status will become - 'requested'

			- this request is visible to wallbox owner
				owner will select the payment method (cash or pre-authorized)

				if pre-authorized:
					- one payment link is generated and linked with that 'charging request'

					- user have to authorize that payment transaction.

					- if authorized transaction then user can see 'schedule charging' btn.

					- user will add schedule date time and after that 'start charging' btn is visible.

					- user will start the charging 
						- request status = 'in_progress'
						- visible 'Complete charging' btn for stop charging

					- after completion of charging it will automatically deduct the actual amount from pre-authorize transaction.

					- after this 'charging status' = 'completed'

				if cash:
					- it will not generate any payment link and it will not check the transaction status.

					- visible 'start charging' btn.

					- when user click on it request_status = 'in_progress'

						- visible 'complete chargign' btn for stop charging

					- when charging stop, request_status = 'completed'

	** Condominium Owner :
		- can see condominium records, in which user is set as a owner
		- can see building records, in which user is set as a owner
		- can see parking space records, in which user is set as a owner

		- can see all the users in which condominium is set and user is condominium owner.
		- can see all the Wallbox Order in which condominium is set and user is condominium owner.
		- can see all the subscription records in which wallbox_order.condominium is set and user is condominium owner.
		- can see all the 'installation records' in which condominium is set and user is condominium owner.
		- can see all the 'request charging' records in which condominium is set and user is condominium owner.
		- can see all the 'Sale Orders' records in which request_charging_id.condominium is set and user is condominium owner.
		- can see all the 'Invoices' records in which sale_order_id.request_charging_id.condominium is set and user is condominium owner.

	** System Admin : 
		- can see all the things of all table records.
